text: Alexander Stewart "Sandy" Fitzpatrick (born December 22, 1944 in Paisley, Scotland) is a retired professional ice hockey player. He played in the in the National Hockey League for the New York Rangers and Minnesota North Stars. == References == * Category:1944 births Category:Living people Category:Minnesota North Stars players Category:New York Rangers players Category:Ice hockey centres Category:Ice hockey people from Ontario
